| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-3156 — Mass File Rename (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 26ad37d9-400d-544d-812c-6c31e1099207"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
